

=Bio=

"Taking an active role in global reform – a philosopher, occasional blogger and outdoor enthusiast living in the mountains of Whistler, BC – I'm Co-Founder, CEO and Creative Strategist to The Citizens Media®  (the-cm.com).  

With a background in network management, since moving from England to Canada in 2001, I've been involved in various ventures, such as developing slogans and ad campaigns, building and running election websites, and (employing members of the First Nations community, Lil'wat) managing a manual snow removal business I co-own."

